### 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 대상 게시글 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userKey}}/posts?page=0
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 팔로워 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userKey}}/followers?page=0
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 팔로잉 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userKey}}/followings?page=0
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 프로필 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "안녕하세요!",
  "email": "updated@petfeed.com"
}

###

### 팔로우
# PATCH → POST/DELETE 분리: HttpURLConnection PATCH 미지원 + REST 시맨틱 명확화
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/following/{{userKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 언팔로우
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/following/{{userKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
